destiny.translation[0].definitions[0].de: the things that will happen to someone in the future, especially those that cannot be changed or controlled
destiny.translation[0].definitions[0].ex: Nancy wondered whether it was her destiny to live in England and marry Melvyn.
destiny.translation[0].definitions[1].de: the power that some people believe decides what will happen to them in the future
